title: Swedish Rye Bread
ingredients: ['450ml (16 fl oz) water', '100g (4 oz) dark brown soft sugar', '2 tablespoons vegetable oil', '1 dessertspoon salt', '1 dessertspoon orange zest', '1 1/2 teaspoons caraway seed', '1 1/2 teaspoons fennel seed', '675g (1 1/2 lb) plain flour', '2 (7g) sachets dried active baking yeast', '2 eggs, room temperature', '200g (7 oz) rye flour']
